B

b - Variable in class network.Edge
b coefficient as used in BPR formula time = freeFlowTime * (1 + b*(flow/capacity)^power
betaLength - Variable in class choiceModel.RUM
The effect of time on cost; on networks like Sioux Falls where the link length is arbitrarily set to be the same as the link free flow travel time, this should be set to 0.
betaPS - Static variable in class choiceModel.MNL
The MNL does not use a path size term in its utility specification, and therefore its path size factor's only appropriate value is 0.
betaPS - Variable in class choiceModel.RUM
Path size parameter with a default value of -3, although many RUMs would not use this value; such RUM should explicitly override the inherited default value with a final value of 0.
betaPS - Static variable in class choiceModel.TMNL
The MNL does not include a path size term, and the inclusion of one should be implemented in a different class (TPSL).
betaTime - Variable in class choiceModel.RUM
Value of time (VoT) used in computeEnumeratorInProbabilityExpression.
